driver.name: GcodeDriver
driver.detected-firmware: FIRMWARE_NAME:Smoothieware, FIRMWARE_URL:http%3A//smoothieware.org, X-SOURCE_CODE_URL:https%3A//github.com/janm012012/Smoothieware-CHMT, FIRMWARE_VERSION:chmt-8fa4a8e0, X-FIRMWARE_BUILD_DATE:Dec 30 2022 15:19:10, X-SYSTEM_CLOCK:168MHz, X-AXES:7, X-PAXES:7, X-GRBL_MODE:0, X-SERIAL_FLOW:NONE, X-CNC:0, X-MSD:1

command.text: M82 ; Set absolute mode for extruder
M84 ; Disable steppers to reset the Z axis
G4P500 ; Wait 500ms for Z axis to settle
G92 X0 Y0 Z0 A0 B0 ; Reset machine coordinates
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
M92 X31.95 Y31.992 ; Set steps per mm
{False:M801 ; close N1 vacuum solenoid / open N1 blower solenoid }
{False:M805 ; close N2 vacuum solenoid / open N2 blower solenoid }
{True: G4 P10} ; wait a little bit until the pin is down
{False: G4 P50} ; wait a little bit until the pin is up (avoid false interlock errors)
{True:G92 C0 G0 C9 ; Set absolute position to 0, Move 9mm ; T2G92C0G0C6}
M80{True:8}{False:9} ; VAC M808 on / M809 off
M81{True:2}{False:3} ; BLOW M812 on / M813 off
M81{True:0}{False:1} ; UPLED M810 on / M811 off
M81{True:4}{False:5} ; DOWNLED M814 on / M815 off
M81{True:8}{False:9} ; CAMSW M818 on / M819 off
{True:G92 D0 G0 D12 ; Set absolute position to 0, Move 12mm ; T3G92E0G0E5}
